+    //       onSizeChanged -> full Chromium relayout.
+    // Fix: reset padding explicitly on hide, and perform a one-frame 1px height
+    // "jiggle" on the content child when the IME transitions visible -> hidden;
+    // the jiggle triggers onSizeChanged in the WebView (rotation-equivalent) which
